header: BRIEF-Nvidia Corp says entered into agreement with Goldman, Sachs & Co. to terminate certain of outstanding warrants
body:
* Nvidia Corp says entered into an agreement with Goldman, Sachs & Co. To terminate certain of outstanding warrants to purchase shares of company’s stock

* Nvidia Corp says pursuant to terms of termination agreement, 63.3 million warrants in aggregate will be terminated Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
